    "body": "> Is there any way to make 2 test files run independent from each other?\r\n\r\nHey @akkien, running tests in parallel (`npx hardhat test --parallel`) will create a different network for each test file.\r\n\r\nAlternatively, you can reset the network with `hardhat_reset` in a `before` hook of each test.",
